OL,5, A retired British geologist has been   
OL,6, jailed for 15 years for attempting to  
OL,7, remove artefacts from Iraq.            
OL,9,FJim Fitton, 66, who is originally from 
OL,10,FBath, collected 12 stones and shards of
OL,11,Fbroken pottery during a recent geology 
OL,12,Fand archaeology tour of the country.   
OL,14,FMr Fitton has insisted he had no idea  
OL,15,Fhe was breaking Iraqi laws.            
OL,17,FThe family of Mr Fitton said they were 
OL,18,F"absolutely shattered" and             
OL,19,F"heartbroken" by the news. They urged  
OL,20,Fthe government to help free him.       
